caption:
Introducing the first in our Ultimate Studio series. 

Meet @zehraibrahim, founder of @theselflovelab.co.uk.

Frustrated by the lack of inclusive wellness spaces in London, Zehra has created a sanctuary for self-care – a space where women can unplug, feel safe, and simply be. 

And when we asked Zehra for her take? 
“My Ultimate Studio is when the sun is shining and I’m in nature – stretching, flowing and feeling the freshness of the outdoors.” 

We’re inspired by you, Zehra 🌿💆‍♀️ 

#ultimatestudio #sweatybetty
